{"tid":549112,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[私服] 新天龍八部 無盡天龍 2018最新仿官 唔怕蝕做 最怕無人玩#","createTime":"2018-02-03T09:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T06:55:48.000Z","uid":122217,"like":15,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5b899e628e9dcef30ac5b0cbea85aea92b282e","tid":549112,"uid":122217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"最新客戶端:<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1hJagdhvCFcb2uQ4DeoiXCrUUHg_lqXtb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1hJagdhvCFcb2uQ4DeoiXCrUUHg_lqXtb&d=BlW%2BZMQ4xO5zio%2BQKUV5mPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=848db74d\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1hJagdhvCFcb2uQ4DeoiXCrUUHg_lqXtb</a><br />\n<br />\nTG谷:<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/GRdquUJsff6ncgi50cviog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FGRdquUJsff6ncgi50cviog&d=BlW%2BZMQ4xO5zio%2BQKUV5mPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=45e4a13e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/GRdquUJsff6ncgi50cviog</a><br />\n<br />\n詳細資訊:<a href=\"http://www.wjtlbb.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wjtlbb.com%2F&d=BlW%2BZMQ4xO5zio%2BQKUV5mPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9855c4e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wjtlbb.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nGM感言:<br />\n版本2018最新仿官 會KEEP住更新 盡量同步官方<br />\n叫無盡天龍原因好簡單 希望長期開放 屹立不倒<br />\n廢話唔多講 開得私服 黎黎去去都係個D設定<br />\n想知詳細D既可以留意上面個網<br />\nGM都諗住同大家一齊由頭開始玩 <br />\n不過我既記憶只係停留到刷棋既時代<br />\n名副其實老屎忽 跟唔上時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔介意有老手玩家教埋我玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果大家想懷舊蠢蠢欲動就唔好諗快D加入<br />\nServer無泡點設定 但盡量都想做到半公益<br />\n升LV會有升級元寶獎勵<br />\n我唔介意蝕住本開落去 只係想有多D人一齊玩<br />\n最好加入TG谷 將來有咩更新乜野都會係入面講 <br />\nGM希望當大家係朋友一齊玩<br />\n玩得開心可以贊助一下都無仿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n商店物品價格都唔算貴<br />\n儲值1:1點=40000元寶<br />\n<br />\n有咩建議歡迎入TG谷傾<br />\n改得到又合理既會考慮下<br />\n因為始終要長期同步官方<br />\n所以盡量都唔想有大改既野<br />\n將來有更新同步既會有Patch發放<br />\n<br />\n諗到有咩活動搞下都可以係TG谷提議下<br />\n例如定時定侯搞下殺GM送元寶活動比大家發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n節日抽獎送下元寶等等<br />\n<br />\n希望大家玩得開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGM好寂寞~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ac15093b23a7430f2769ccfcf73f259823a0f7","tid":549112,"uid":161581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"不了 快閃服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c41acb947c11bd65719ba894ede1e8cb7d17c32","tid":549112,"uid":122217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6ac15093b23a7430f2769ccfcf73f259823a0f7","tid":549112,"uid":161581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"不了 快閃服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"閃唔閃睇耐啲未知 <br />\n不過開私服都幾慘<br />\n未夠半日就比人DDOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6602793da01789ae48cc0dc346e8d2b563f10c7","tid":549112,"uid":122217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"TG Channel:<a href=\"https://t.me/wjtlbb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwjtlbb&d=BlW%2BZMQ4xO5zio%2BQKUV5mPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ff0a2d5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wjtlbb</a><br />\n<br />\n新增活動:<br />\n2018-02-04<br />\n玩家119等 送VIP1加40萬元寶 請聯絡GM發放"},{"pid":"69f52b8ed78f4784346f700003787fa28d39af5a","tid":549112,"uid":127991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"課幾多可以全9？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n課金有冇稱號果啲 有冇多啲details <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f6fdbc709bed898f56870a162044c9c70029a9","tid":549112,"uid":12